summary: i wanted to ask/say something: why does everyone hate brie larson?? i mean look at her she is so beautiful and talented and i...
body:
i wanted to ask/say something: why does everyone hate brie larson?? i mean look at her she is so beautiful and talented and i just don’t understand

i’m not gonna lie at first i didn’t like her at ALL because i saw a post that said she was going to replace captain america as captain marvel and i just didn’t want that to happen BUT then i remembered i cannot judge HER because of that and then i saw this post about how she can’t act and again i thought what if they’re right? but then i remembered i cannot judge HER ACTING if i haven’t seen it before so i watched room and bitch it was so good she did amazing and she literally got a fucking award for it so why do people say she can’t act?

and all this shit like ‘she isn’t a good captain marvel’ ‘she look too serious in the promo pictures of captain marvel’ and ‘she should smile more’ WHAT KIND OF BULLSHIT IS THAT??? you haven’t seen the film so how the FUCK would you know if she isn’t a good captain marvel and she looks serious and doesn’t smile in the promos up till now because … IT’S HER CHARACTER CAROL DANVERS AKA CAPTAIN MARVEL IN THE PROMOS she is absolutely amazing and awesome and perfect and all the other good things you can think of and she doesn’t deserve all this fucking hate

fuck y’all haters
